{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":[" "],"fields":{"title":{"boost":1000.0},"text":{"boost":1.0},"tags":{"boost":1000000.0}}},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"AI Data Platform Study","text":"<p>AI Data Platform \uad6c\ucd95 \ubc0f Local LLM \uc5f0\uad6c\ub97c \uc704\ud55c \uc2a4\ud130\ub514 \ud504\ub85c\uc81d\ud2b8\uc785\ub2c8\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"#_1","title":"\ubaa9\ud45c","text":"<ul> <li>Data Lakehouse \uc774\ud574</li> <li>Iceberg \uc774\ud574</li> <li>Spark \uc774\ud574</li> <li>Trino \uc774\ud574</li> <li>Local LLM \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>RAG \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>Agent \uad6c\ucd95</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#_2","title":"\ud559\uc2b5 \uc21c\uc11c","text":"<ol> <li>Data Platform</li> <li>Data Lakehouse</li> <li>Iceberg</li> <li>Spark</li> <li>Trino</li> <li>Local LLM</li> <li>RAG</li> <li>Agent</li> </ol>"},{"location":"index_old/","title":"Welcome to MkDocs","text":"<p>For full documentation visit mkdocs.org.</p>"},{"location":"index_old/#commands","title":"Commands","text":"<ul> <li><code>mkdocs new [dir-name]</code> - Create a new project.</li> <li><code>mkdocs serve</code> - Start the live-reloading docs server.</li> <li><code>mkdocs build</code> - Build the documentation site.</li> <li><code>mkdocs -h</code> - Print help message and exit.</li> </ul>"},{"location":"index_old/#project-layout","title":"Project layout","text":"<pre><code>mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.\ndocs/\n    index.md  # The documentation homepage.\n    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/","title":"AI Data Platform &amp; Local LLM Study Roadmap","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#1","title":"1. \uc2a4\ud130\ub514 \uac1c\uc694","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_1","title":"\ubaa9\uc801","text":"<p>\ubcf8 \uc2a4\ud130\ub514\ub294 ChatGPT\uc640 \uac19\uc740 \uc0dd\uc131\ud615 AI\ub97c \ub2e8\uc21c\ud788 \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud558\ub294 \uc218\uc900\uc744 \ub118\uc5b4,</p> <ul> <li>Local LLM \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>RAG(Retrieval Augmented Generation) \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>AI Agent \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>AI \ub370\uc774\ud130 \ud50c\ub7ab\ud3fc \uc124\uacc4</li> <li>LLM Serving \ud50c\ub7ab\ud3fc \uad6c\ucd95</li> </ul> <p>\uc5ed\ub7c9\uc744 \ud655\ubcf4\ud558\uc5ec AI \ud50c\ub7ab\ud3fc \uc544\ud0a4\ud14d\ud2b8 \uc218\uc900\uc758 \uae30\uc220 \uc774\ud574\ub97c \ubaa9\ud45c\ub85c \ud55c\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_2","title":"\ucd5c\uc885 \ubaa9\ud45c","text":"<p>\ub2e4\uc74c\uacfc \uac19\uc740 AI \uc11c\ube44\uc2a4\ub97c \uc9c1\uc811 \uad6c\ucd95\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub294 \uc218\uc900\uc5d0 \ub3c4\ub2ec\ud55c\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#ai","title":"AI \ube44\uc11c","text":"<ul> <li>\uc81c\uc548\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9</li> <li>PPT \uac80\uc0c9</li> <li>RFP \uac80\uc0c9</li> <li>\ud68c\uc758\ub85d \uac80\uc0c9</li> <li>\uae30\uc220\ubb38\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#ai-agent","title":"AI Agent","text":"<ul> <li>\uc7a5\ud45c \ucd08\uc548 \uc0dd\uc131</li> <li>\ubb38\uc11c \uc694\uc57d</li> <li>API \ubb38\uc11c \uc0dd\uc131</li> <li>\uc81c\uc548\uc11c \uc791\uc131 \uc9c0\uc6d0</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#ai_1","title":"AI \ud50c\ub7ab\ud3fc","text":"<ul> <li>\ub370\uc774\ud130 \uc218\uc9d1</li> <li>\ub370\uc774\ud130 \uc800\uc7a5</li> <li>\ub370\uc774\ud130 \ubd84\uc11d</li> <li>AI \uc11c\ube44\uc2a4 \uc81c\uacf5</li> </ul> <p>\uc804\uccb4 \uc544\ud0a4\ud14d\ucc98\ub97c \uc124\uacc4\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub294 \uc218\uc900 \ud655\ubcf4</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#step-1-local-llm","title":"STEP 1. Local LLM \uc2dc\uc791","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_3","title":"\ubaa9\ud45c","text":"<p>\ud074\ub77c\uc6b0\ub4dc \uae30\ubc18 AI\uac00 \uc544\ub2cc \uac1c\uc778 PC\uc5d0\uc11c LLM\uc744 \uc9c1\uc811 \uc2e4\ud589\ud558\uc5ec LLM \ub3d9\uc791 \uc6d0\ub9ac\ub97c \uc774\ud574\ud55c\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_4","title":"\uc65c \ubc30\uc6b0\ub294\uac00?","text":"<p>ChatGPT\ub97c \uc0ac\uc6a9\ud558\uba74 AI\uac00 \uc5b4\ub5bb\uac8c \ub3d9\uc791\ud558\ub294\uc9c0 \ubcf4\uc774\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294\ub2e4.</p> <p>\ub85c\uceec \ud658\uacbd\uc5d0\uc11c \uc9c1\uc811 \ubaa8\ub378\uc744 \uc2e4\ud589\ud558\uba74</p> <ul> <li>\ubaa8\ub378 \ud06c\uae30</li> <li>\uba54\ubaa8\ub9ac \uc0ac\uc6a9\ub7c9</li> <li>\uc751\ub2f5 \uc18d\ub3c4</li> <li>\ucd94\ub860 \uacfc\uc815</li> </ul> <p>\ub4f1\uc744 \uccb4\ud5d8\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_5","title":"\uc2e4\uc2b5","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#ollama","title":"Ollama \uc124\uce58","text":"<pre><code>brew install ollama\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_6","title":"\ubaa8\ub378 \uc2e4\ud589","text":"<pre><code>ollama run qwen3:8b\n</code></pre> <pre><code>ollama run gemma3:12b\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_7","title":"\ud559\uc2b5 \ub0b4\uc6a9","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#llm","title":"LLM \uac1c\ub150","text":"<ul> <li>Transformer</li> <li>Token</li> <li>Attention</li> <li>Context Window</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_8","title":"\ubaa8\ub378 \ud06c\uae30","text":"<ul> <li>3B</li> <li>7B</li> <li>14B</li> <li>32B</li> <li>70B</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_9","title":"\ubaa8\ub378 \ucd5c\uc801\ud654","text":"<ul> <li>Quantization</li> <li>Q4</li> <li>Q8</li> <li>GGUF</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#prompt-engineering","title":"Prompt Engineering","text":"<ul> <li>Zero Shot</li> <li>Few Shot</li> <li>Chain of Thought</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_10","title":"\uacb0\uacfc\ubb3c","text":"<ul> <li>\ub85c\uceec AI \ucc57\ubd07 \uad6c\ucd95</li> <li>\ub2e4\uc591\ud55c \ubaa8\ub378 \uc131\ub2a5 \ube44\uad50</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#step-2-rag","title":"STEP 2. RAG \uad6c\ucd95","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_11","title":"\ubaa9\ud45c","text":"<p>AI\uac00 \ubb38\uc11c\ub97c \uac80\uc0c9\ud558\uc5ec \ub2f5\ubcc0\ud558\ub3c4\ub85d \ub9cc\ub4e0\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_12","title":"\uc65c \ubc30\uc6b0\ub294\uac00?","text":"<p>LLM\uc740 \ud559\uc2b5\ub418\uc9c0 \uc54a\uc740 \uc0ac\ub0b4 \ubb38\uc11c\ub97c \uc54c \uc218 \uc5c6\ub2e4.</p> <p>\ub530\ub77c\uc11c</p> <ul> <li>\uc81c\uc548\uc11c</li> <li>PPT</li> <li>PDF</li> <li>\uc6b4\uc601\ubb38\uc11c</li> </ul> <p>\ub97c AI\uac00 \uac80\uc0c9\ud560 \uc218 \uc788\ub3c4\ub85d \ud574\uc57c \ud55c\ub2e4.</p> <p>\uc774\ub97c RAG\ub77c\uace0 \ud55c\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_13","title":"\uac1c\ub150","text":"<pre><code>\ubb38\uc11c\n\n\u2193\n\nChunking\n\n\u2193\n\nEmbedding\n\n\u2193\n\nVector DB\n\n\u2193\n\n\uac80\uc0c9\n\n\u2193\n\nLLM \ub2f5\ubcc0 \uc0dd\uc131\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_14","title":"\uc2e4\uc2b5","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_15","title":"\ub370\uc774\ud130","text":"<ul> <li>PDF</li> <li>PPTX</li> <li>DOCX</li> <li>Markdown</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#embedding","title":"Embedding","text":"<ul> <li>BGE</li> <li>Nomic</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#vector-db","title":"Vector DB","text":"<ul> <li>ChromaDB</li> <li>Qdrant</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_16","title":"\ud559\uc2b5 \ub0b4\uc6a9","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#chunking","title":"Chunking","text":"<p>\ubb38\uc11c\ub97c \uc801\uc808\ud55c \ud06c\uae30\ub85c \ubd84\ud560</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#embedding_1","title":"Embedding","text":"<p>\ubb38\uc7a5\uc744 \ubca1\ud130\ub85c \ubcc0\ud658</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#similarity-search","title":"Similarity Search","text":"<p>\uc9c8\ubb38\uacfc \uac00\uc7a5 \uc720\uc0ac\ud55c \ubb38\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#vector-database","title":"Vector Database","text":"<p>\ubca1\ud130 \uc800\uc7a5 \ubc0f \uac80\uc0c9</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_17","title":"\uacb0\uacfc\ubb3c","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_18","title":"\uc81c\uc548\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9 \uc2dc\uc2a4\ud15c","text":"<p>\uc608\uc2dc</p> <pre><code>\uc9c8\ubb38\n\n\"\ud55c\uad6d\uc7a5\ud559\uc7ac\ub2e8 API \uad6c\ucd95 \uad00\ub828 \ub0b4\uc6a9\uc744 \uc54c\ub824\uc918\"\n\n\u2193\n\n\uacfc\uac70 \uc81c\uc548\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9\n\n\u2193\n\n\uadfc\uac70 \uc81c\uc2dc\n\n\u2193\n\n\ub2f5\ubcc0 \uc0dd\uc131\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#step-3-ai-agent","title":"STEP 3. AI Agent \uad6c\ucd95","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_19","title":"\ubaa9\ud45c","text":"<p>AI\uac00 \uc2a4\uc2a4\ub85c \uc791\uc5c5\uc744 \uc218\ud589\ud558\ub3c4\ub85d \ub9cc\ub4e0\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_20","title":"\uc65c \ubc30\uc6b0\ub294\uac00?","text":"<p>\uc77c\ubc18 LLM\uc740 \uc9c8\ubb38\uc5d0 \ub300\ud55c \ub2f5\ubcc0\ub9cc \ud55c\ub2e4.</p> <p>Agent\ub294</p> <ul> <li>\uac80\uc0c9</li> <li>\ud310\ub2e8</li> <li>\uc2e4\ud589</li> </ul> <p>\uc744 \uc218\ud589\ud55c\ub2e4.</p>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_21","title":"\uc608\uc2dc","text":"<pre><code>\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790\n\n\u2193\n\n\uc7a5\ud559\uc7ac\ub2e8 API \uad00\ub828 \uc7a5\ud45c \uc791\uc131\n\n\u2193\n\n\uad00\ub828 \ubb38\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9\n\n\u2193\n\nRFP \uac80\uc0c9\n\n\u2193\n\n\uc720\uc0ac \uc81c\uc548\uc11c \uac80\uc0c9\n\n\u2193\n\n\uc7a5\ud45c \ucd08\uc548 \uc0dd\uc131\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#_22","title":"\ud559\uc2b5 \ub0b4\uc6a9","text":""},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#agent","title":"Agent","text":"<ul> <li>Tool Calling</li> <li>Planning</li> <li>Reasoning</li> <li>Memory</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#framework","title":"Framework","text":"<ul> <li>LangChain</li> <li>LangGraph</li> </ul>"},{"location":"roadmap/study-roadmap/#mcp","title":"MCP","text":"<p>Model Context